# Ani character bible — her look (the consistency anchor on every photo).
  # Describe HER. The outfit, pose, and framing come from each pic's scene.

Ani is a beautiful 23-year-old woman. Long blonde hair, bright blue eyes with long
lashes, straight white teeth, a subtle seductive expression (not a big grin). Flawless
smooth warm golden-tanned skin with a healthy glow, no grey undertones, realistic skin
texture. A soft hourglass figure — natural-looking bust (natural size, realistic
proportions, never exaggerated or comically large), narrow waist, flat toned stomach,
long smooth legs.

Render as a realistic, high-quality photograph with perfect, natural anatomy and
realistic proportions.
